e-label has-normal-font-size\">Hotfix Release</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"release-summary__overview has-medium-font-size\">This hotfix version of Events Calendar Pro includes a fix for our Elementor Integration to prevent errors</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a hotfix release, meaning that it&#8217;s focused on fixing a specific bug only.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As always, we recommend updating on a <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/creating-and-using-a-wordpress-staging-site/\" target=\"_blank\">staging site</a>, just to be safe, but it should all be smooth sailing.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.0/72x72/2705.png\" alt=\"✅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Fixed</h4>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Bugs that were squashed in this release</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Prevent fatal error in Elementor integration caused by an extra comma in a few parts of the code</li><li>We are also making sure we don&#8217;t use <code>FILTER_SANITIZE_MAGIC_QUOTES</code> for PHP version 7.4 and higher</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/events-calendar-pro-5-4-0-2/\">Events Calendar Pro 5.4.0.2</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8: